examples.en: Barbara and I had a nice long visit.
Barbara spun past in her new sportscar.
Barbara answered with her customary enthusiasm.
Barbara's getting on really well at her new job.
'We could invite John and Barbara.' 'Yes, why not?'
I've known Barbara for years. Since we were babies, actually.
We should hire another secretary to lighten Barbara's workload.
Barbara has a magic touch in the garden (=she grows things very well).
Elton John gave an interview to Barbara Walters (=he answered her questions).
'I'm going to Barbara's house.' 'Like fun you are! Come and finish your chores first.'
